[Name] LibEV
[Summary] A full-featured and high-performance event loop 
[Description] A full-featured and high-performance event loop that is loosely modelled after libevent, but without its limitations and bugs. It is used, among others, in the GNU Virtual Private Ethernet and rxvt-unicode packages, and in the Deliantra MORPG Server and Client 
[License] BSD or GPL 2+ 
[Homepage] http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/libev.html 
